"    Effects of dynamic intrathoracic airway obstruction",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 327px; height: 266px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Left panel, during forced expiration, the intrathoracic intratracheal pressure (P",
"    <sub>",
